<form>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#3333FF"><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 16.0pt; font-family: Arial">系统</span><span style="font-size: 16.0pt; font-family: Arial">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="javascript:print();"><img border="0" src="../image/Printer.gif" align="center" width="82" height="44"></a></span></b></font><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">使用<i>系统</i>屏幕可以启用路由器的各种常规功能，从恢复出厂默认值到启用其远程管理功能等。 </span>
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
<table class="MsoNormalTable" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-collapse: collapse; border: medium none">
  <tr>
    <td width="115" valign="top" style="width: 86.4pt; border: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm">
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">恢复出厂默认值</span></b></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></b></td>
    <td width="475" valign="top" style="width: 356.4pt; border-left: medium none; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm">
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">单击<b>是</b>按钮可将所有配置设置重置为其默认值，然后单击<b>应用</b>按钮。注意：恢复默认设置时将丢失已保存的所有设置。默认情况下该功能处于禁用状态。</span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="115" valign="top" style="width: 86.4pt; border-left: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top: medium none; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm">
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">升级固件</span></b></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></b></td>
    <td width="475" valign="top" style="width: 356.4pt; border-left: medium none; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top: medium none; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm">
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">单击<b>升级</b>按钮可将新的固件加载到路由器上。新的固件版本将在<i> www.linksys.com</i> 上发布，并可免费进行下载。如果路由器没有出现问题，则无需下载更新的固件版本，除非新版本中包含您要使用的新增功能。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">注意：在升级路由器的固件时，可能会丢失其配置设置，因此，请确保在升级固件之前，先写下路由器的设置。</span></b></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">要升级路由器的固件，请执行以下操作：</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">1.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">从 Linksys 网站下载固件升级文件。 </span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">2.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">解压缩固件升级文件。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">3.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">单击<b>升级</b>按钮。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">4.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">在<i>固件升级</i>屏幕上，单击<b>浏览</b>按钮，以查找固件升级文件。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">5.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">双击固件升级文件。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">6.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">单击<b>升级</b>按钮，然后按照屏幕上的指导执行操作。 </span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">注意：在升级固件时，请不要关闭路由器的电源或按重置按钮。</span></b></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="115" valign="top" style="width: 86.4pt; border-left: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top: medium none; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm">
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">多播通过</span></b></td>
    <td width="475" valign="top" style="width: 356.4pt; border-left: medium none; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top: medium none; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm">
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">在将单个数据传输同时发送给多个接收方时，会出现 IP 多播。&nbsp; 通过使用多播通过功能，路由器可允许将 IP 多播包转发到适当的计算机。保持默认设置<b>启用</b>以支持该功能，或选择<b>禁用</b>以禁用该功能。</span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="115" valign="top" style="width: 86.4pt; border-left: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top: medium none; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm">
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">MAC 克隆</span></b></td>
    <td width="475" valign="top" style="width: 356.4pt; border-left: medium none; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top: medium none; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm">
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">路由器的 MAC 地址是 12 个数字的代码，该代码指定给硬件的唯一片段以便进行标识。一些 ISP 要求注册网卡/适配器的 MAC 	地址，该网卡/适配器在安装期间会连接到电缆或 DSL 调制解调器。如果您的 ISP 要求进行 MAC 地址注册，请按照 PC 操作系统的指导来查找适配器的 MAC 地址。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">对于 Windows 98 和 Millennium：</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">1.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>单击</span><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">开始</span></b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">按钮，然后选择</span><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">运行</span></b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">2.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>在提供的字段中键入 </span><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">winipcfg</span></b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">，然后按</span><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">确定</span></b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">键。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">3.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>选择所使用的以太网适配器。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">4.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>单击</span><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">更多信息</span></b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">5.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>写下适配器的 MAC 地址。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">对于 Windows 2000 和 XP：</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">1.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>单击</span><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">开始</span></b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">按钮，然后选择</span><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">运行</span></b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">2.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>在提供的字段中键入 </span><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">cmd</span></b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">，然后按</span><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">确定</span></b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">键。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">3.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>在命令提示符下，运行 </span><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">ipconfig /all</span></b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">，并查看适配器的物理地址。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">4.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>写下适配器的 MAC 地址。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">要将网络适配器的 MAC 地址克隆到路由器上，并且不想请求 ISP 来更改注册的 MAC 地址，请遵循以下指导：</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">1.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>选择</span><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">启用</span></b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">2.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>在 <i>MAC 地址</i>字段中输入适配器的 MAC 地址。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 18.0pt">
<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">3.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>单击</span><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">应用</span></b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">按钮。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">要禁用 MAC 地址克隆，请保持默认设置</span><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">禁用</span></b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family: Arial">。</span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="115" valign="top" style="width: 86.4pt; border-left: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top: medium none; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm">
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">远程管理</span></b></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></b></td>
    <td width="475" valign="top" style="width: 356.4pt; border-left: medium none; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top: medium none; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm">
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">使用此功能可以通过 Internet 从远程位置管理路由器。&nbsp;要禁用此功能，请保持默认设置<b>禁用</b>。要启用此功能，请选择<b>启用</b>，然后使用 PC 上的指定端口（默认值为 <b>8080</b>）来远程管理路由器。如果您尚未将路由器的默认口令更改为自己所选的口令，则此时必须进行更改。独特的口令可以提高安全性。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">要远程管理路由器，请在 Web 浏览器的<i>地址</i>字段中输入 <b>http://xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx:8080</b>（其中 x 表示路由器的 Internet IP 地址，而 8080 表示指定的端口）。此时系统将要求您提供路由器的口令。成功输入口令后，即可访问路由器基于 Web 的实用程序。</span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">注意：如果启用了远程管理功能，则知道路由器 Internet IP 地址和口令的任何人均可更改路由器的设置。</span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="115" valign="top" style="width: 86.4pt; border-left: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top: medium none; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm">
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">MTU</span></b></td>
    <td width="475" valign="top" style="width: 356.4pt; border-left: medium none; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top: medium none; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm">
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">MTU 为最大传输单元。该设置指定 Internet 传输允许的最大包大小。保持默认设置<b>自动</b>，以使路由器为 Internet 连接选择最佳 MTU。要指定 MTU 大小，请选择<b>手动</b>，然后输入所需的值（默认设置为 <b>1400</b>）。&nbsp;该值应在 1200 到 1500 之间。</span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="115" valign="top" style="width: 86.4pt; border-left: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top: medium none; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm">
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">日志</span></b></td>
    <td width="475" valign="top" style="width: 356.4pt; border-left: medium none; border-right: 1.0pt solid windowtext; border-top: medium none; border-bottom: 1.0pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm">
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">路由器可以保留 Internet 连接的所有传入或传出流量日志。要保留活动日志，请选择<b>启用</b>。要查看路由器最近传入流量的临时日志，请单击<b>传入访问日志</b>按钮。要查看路由器最近传出流量的临时日志，请单击<b>传出访问日志</b>按钮。</span></td>
  </tr>
</table>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:Arial">选中所有值并单击<b>应用</b>可保存您的设置。单击<b>取消</b>可取消未保存的更改。</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
